    },

    "final_verdict": "VeriVox demonstrates strong potential with a score of 7.5/10. The project shows significant innovation and technical merit, but requires attention to several key areas: 1) Develop a clear monetization strategy and market approach, 2) Simplify technical architecture to reduce maintenance burden, 3) Conduct and present user testing results, 4) Address privacy concerns explicitly, 5) Create a more gradual onboarding process for non-technical users. The core concept is valuable and well-executed, but success will depend on addressing these practical concerns while maintaining the project's innovative spirit."
